top. And people would take that out
and use it in their coffee.

00:17:36.770 --> 00:17:40.990
And then you'd have what's
effectively skim milk on the bottom.

00:17:40.990 --> 00:17:45.220
So, somebody came up with the idea,
obviously somebody who had studied

00:17:45.220 --> 00:17:49.440
the rudiments of physical chemistry,
and reasoned that if the fatty phase

